---
import CaseStudyLayout from "../layouts/CaseStudyLayout.astro";
---

<CaseStudyLayout
  title="Truist — Digital Banking Platform"
  description="How I built and scaled a 30-person design org at SunTrust across all lines of business, then led business and commercial banking design through the $66B merger to Truist."
  ogImage="/images/truist/1771246115132-cd678175.png"
>
  <style>
    :root {
      --truist-purple: #3b1a5a;
      --truist-deep: #2d1446;
      --truist-teal: #00b4a0;
      --warm-white: #f7f5f2;
      --soft-purple: #f3eff8;
      --text-primary: #1a1a1a;
      --text-secondary: #5a5a5a;
      --text-light: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
      --accent: #3b1a5a;
    }

    /* ── Hero ── */
    .hero {
      position: relative;
      min-height: 90vh;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      text-align: center;
      background: linear-gradient(
        135deg,
        #1d0b2e 0%,
        var(--truist-purple) 50%,
        #512678 100%
      );
      overflow: hidden;
      padding: 160px 80px;
    }

    .hero::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      top: -20%;
      right: -10%;
      width: 800px;
      height: 800px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: radial-gradient(
        circle,
        rgba(0, 180, 160, 0.1) 0%,
        transparent 70%
      );
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .hero-left {
      max-width: 840px;
      z-index: 1;
      margin-bottom: 80px;
    }

    .hero-right {
      z-index: 1;
      width: 100%;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .hero-right img {
      max-height: 520px;
      width: auto;
      border-radius: 32px;
      box-shadow: 0 64px 128px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
      background: #000;
    }

    .hero-label {
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 4px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--truist-teal);
      margin-bottom: 32px;
    }

    .hero-title {
      font-family: "Playfair Display", serif;
      font-size: clamp(48px, 6vw, 80px);
      font-weight: 400;
      color: #fff;
      line-height: 1.05;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }

    .hero-subtitle {
      font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: 300;
      color: var(--text-light);
      line-height: 1.75;
      max-width: 640px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    /* ── Ecosystem Strip ── */
    .ecosystem {
      background: var(--soft-purple);
      padding: 160px 80px;
    }

    .ecosystem-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 40px;
      margin-top: 80px;
      max-width: 1300px;
      margin-left: auto;
      margin-right: auto;
    }

    .eco-card {
      background: #fff;
      border-radius: 12px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 32px rgba(59, 26, 90, 0.05);
      transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.2, 0.8, 0.2, 1);
      border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.03);
    }

    .eco-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-8px);
      box-shadow: 0 32px 64px rgba(59, 26, 90, 0.1);
    }

    .eco-card img {
      width: 100%;
      display: block;
    }

    .eco-card-text {
      padding: 32px;
    }

    .eco-card-text h3 {
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: var(--text-primary);
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .eco-card-text p {
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 300;
      color: var(--text-secondary);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    /* ── Dark showcase ── */
    .showcase-dark {
      background: var(--truist-deep);
      padding: 160px 80px;
    }

    .showcase-dark .section-label {
      color: var(--truist-teal);
    }
    .showcase-dark .section-heading {
      color: #fff;
    }
    .showcase-dark .section-body {
      color: var(--text-light);
    }

    .showcase-row {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 64px;
      margin-top: 80px;
      max-width: 1300px;
      margin-left: auto;
      margin-right: auto;
    }

    .showcase-card {
      border-radius: 8px;
      overflow: hidden;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
      transition: all 0.4s ease;
    }

    .showcase-card img {
      width: 100%;
      display: block;
    }

    .showcase-card-text {
      padding: 32px;
    }

    .showcase-card-text h3 {
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: #fff;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }

    .showcase-card-text p {
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 300;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);
    }

    /* ── Wealth / Enterprise ── */
    .wealth {
      background: var(--warm-white);
      padding: 160px 80px;
    }

    .wealth-hero-img {
      margin-top: 80px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 32px 100px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12);
      max-width: 1300px;
      margin-left: auto;
      margin-right: auto;
      background: #fff;
    }

    .wealth-hero-img img {
      width: 100%;
      display: block;
    }

    /* ── Responsive ── */
    @media (max-width: 1024px) {
      .hero {
        padding: 120px 32px;
      }
      .hero-left {
        margin-bottom: 48px;
      }
      .hero-right img {
        max-height: 480px;
      }
      .ecosystem-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
      .ecosystem {
        padding: 100px 32px;
      }
      .showcase-dark {
        padding: 100px 32px;
      }
      .showcase-row {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        gap: 48px;
      }
      .wealth {
        padding: 100px 32px;
      }
    }
  </style>

  <!-- Hero -->
  <div class="hero">
    <div class="hero-left">
      <div class="hero-label">Truist Financial</div>
      <h1 class="hero-title">
        Defining the Digital Experience for America's 7th Largest Bank
      </h1>
      <p class="hero-subtitle">
        I built and scaled a 30-person design organization at SunTrust — owning
        every line of business — then led business and commercial banking design
        through the largest bank merger since 2008.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-right">
      <img
        src="/images/truist/truist-mobile-app-tour-620x1150.jpg"
        alt="Truist mobile app screens"
      />
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Context -->
  <section class="context">
    <div class="context-inner">
      <div>
        <div class="section-label">The Challenge</div>
        <h2 class="section-heading">
          Scaling a design practice ahead of a $66B merger.
        </h2>
        <p class="section-body">
          I inherited a nascent UX team at SunTrust with no research function
          and no independent design voice. I scaled it to a 30-person
          multidisciplinary organization covering Consumer, Small Business,
          Wealth Management, and Commercial Banking. I rebooted the SunTrust
          Innovation Accelerator Studio—introducing strategic foresight and
          presenting future-of-banking scenarios to the C-Suite that informed
          merger strategy. When the $66B merger with BB&T created Truist, I led
          the UX methodology and design execution for business and commercial
          banking across the newly merged entity.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="meta-grid">
          <div class="meta-item">
            <h4>My Role</h4>
            <p>Head of UX Design &amp; Research</p>
          </div>
          <div class="meta-item">
            <h4>Company</h4>
            <p>SunTrust → Truist Financial</p>
          </div>
          <div class="meta-item">
            <h4>Scope</h4>
            <p>
              All lines of business (SunTrust); Business &amp; Commercial
              Banking (Truist); Design System
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="meta-item">
            <h4>Team</h4>
            <p>UX/UI Designers, Researchers, Product Managers, Engineering</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Ecosystem -->
  <div class="ecosystem">
    <div class="section-label">The Ecosystem</div>
    <h2 class="section-heading">Architecting experience at scale.</h2>
    <p class="section-body">
      I led UX design and research across the entirety of SunTrust's digital
      footprint. Managing at this scale required establishing an evidence-based
      design methodology and successfully integrating the voice of the customer
      into a Scaled Agile Framework (SAFe) environment.
    </p>

    <div class="ecosystem-grid">
      <div class="eco-card">
        <img
          src="/images/truist/1771246123096-e2ad64a0.png"
          alt="Truist mobile home screen"
        />
        <div class="eco-card-text">
          <h3>Consumer Mobile</h3>
          <p>
            Account management, transfers, and day-to-day banking designed for
            speed and clarity.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="eco-card">
        <img
          src="/images/truist/f6b34fae57ddb0e3fc45c70cca0e5130.webp"
          alt="Truist business banking dashboard"
        />
        <div class="eco-card-text">
          <h3>Business Banking</h3>
          <p>
            Multi-account management, notifications, and commercial tools for
            business clients.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="eco-card">
        <img
          src="/images/truist/1771246117084-2367c12e.png"
          alt="Truist dashboard on laptop"
        />
        <div class="eco-card-text">
          <h3>Web Platform</h3>
          <p>
            Full-featured dashboard with spending analytics, account activity,
            and cross-product visibility.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Dark Showcase: App Depth -->
  <div class="showcase-dark">
    <div class="section-label">Post-Merger Integration</div>
    <h2 class="section-heading">
      Translating brand into a universal design system.
    </h2>
    <p class="section-body">
      Following the merger, I directed the teams responsible for translating the
      new Truist brand into comprehensive visual design and UI standards. We
      defined and deployed the Truist design system across all digital products
      for the newly merged entity.
    </p>

    <div class="showcase-row">
      <div class="showcase-card">
        <img
          src="/images/truist/1771281467064-e8609008.png"
          alt="Truist app interaction flows"
        />
        <div class="showcase-card-text">
          <h3>Systems Architecture</h3>
          <p>
            Oversaw the structural integration of two legacy banking systems
            into a unified UI pattern library.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="showcase-card">
        <img
          src="/images/truist/1771281469482-048153c4.png"
          alt="Truist cross-device payments"
        />
        <div class="showcase-card-text">
          <h3>Cross-Platform Scale</h3>
          <p>
            Managed strategy for responsive deployment across mobile, web, and
            internal banking portals.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="showcase-row" style="margin-top: 48px;">
      <div class="showcase-card">
        <img
          src="/images/truist/1771281472014-694a3592.png"
          alt="Truist biometric security"
        />
        <div class="showcase-card-text">
          <h3>Methodology Integration</h3>
          <p>
            Embedded dedicated research and design roles into SAFe agile pods.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="showcase-card">
        <img
          src="/images/truist/1771246115132-cd678175.png"
          alt="Truist responsive design system"
        />
        <div class="showcase-card-text">
          <h3>Enterprise Standards</h3>
          <p>Established the governance models for the Truist design system.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Accelerator Feature -->
  <div class="feature-row">
    <div class="feature-image">
      <img
        src="/images/truist/1771281481615-23cda954.jpg"
        alt="Truist onboarding flow on laptop"
      />
    </div>
    <div class="feature-text">
      <div class="section-label">Innovation Leadership</div>
      <h2 class="section-heading">The Innovation Accelerator Studio.</h2>
      <p class="section-body">
        Beyond production software, I rebooted and repositioned the SunTrust
        Innovation Accelerator Studio. I introduced service design, customer
        journey mapping, and strategic foresight as core
        competencies—culminating in an executive foresight exercise that shaped
        the organizational vision ahead of the merger.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Wealth Management -->
  <section class="wealth">
    <div class="section-label">Commercial & Wealth</div>
    <h2 class="section-heading">Strategic Business Lines.</h2>
    <p class="section-body">
      I exclusively led the UX domain for Small Business and Commercial Banking
      through the Truist transition, directing teams to design the tools that
      manage high-value portfolios and enterprise operational capital.
    </p>
    <div class="wealth-hero-img">
      <img
        src="/images/truist/original.png"
        alt="Truist wealth management dashboard"
      />
    </div>
  </section>
</CaseStudyLayout>
